{
  "stem": "5388.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody had to teach you nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You knew it already because you were doing it every week, 52-- 52 weeks a year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I personally never felt any kind of animosity or any sense of anti-Semitism or so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't affected by it as much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember in the '30s, at one time already, somebody came to school to pick me up because there was some trouble where there were some rabble-rousers or somebody there, that's about-- there was some big sign across the street, 'Don't buy from Jews.' But that was already in '30-- '36, '37.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Pilsudski's death, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Pilsudski was pretty decent and very nice to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was already the influence with Hitler, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was-- keep in mind, we were a small Jewish community, about 50 families or so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, must have been a long, long time because my father was born there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was born there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now you're talking 19-- end of 19th century.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were around there for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, Father used to say, 'My America is here.' I think after talking to my sister, she kind of indicated to me that Daddy was worried about that he will be like a deaf and mute person.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They'll-- Yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he-- the language, he was afraid and worried about the language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm surprised at him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he knew-- he knew German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He knew Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But be that as it may, supposedly that was one of the reasons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And maybe my sister, the eldest, would have come, perhaps, to this-- to the World Exhibit in 1939 in New York.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But somehow or other, her cousin, he was religious and the military.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he went in.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
